[Cite as 02106/2003 Case Announcements, 2003-Ohio-541.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

February 6, 2003

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2002-2164. Renwand v. Brush Wellman, Inc.

Cuyahoga App. No. 80843, 2002-Ohio-5849. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
